  "title": "Default theme",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\n\r\nLinked to #2193\r\n\r\nBuild now export two more files: `instantsearch-theme-algolia.css` and `instantsearch-theme-algolia.min.css`\r\n\r\nThe theme is a port of `react-instantsearch-theme-algolia.css` to fit with the actual DOM of is.js widgets.\r\n\r\n**Result**\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/893837/27224996-74bd098c-5298-11e7-91d7-360d6ca84c8b.png)\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/893837/27225005-7d9801ba-5298-11e7-8b8e-96e35cec3bbd.png)\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/893837/27225008-855ddc76-5298-11e7-942e-ee2399f2e96a.png)",
